      "name": "Leaflet Map Configuration Field",
      "summary": "The Leaflet Map Configuration defines a field type for customizing map display settings within a card or form. Its primary purpose is to allow users to specify map configuration options, such as setting a custom tile server URL, to control how maps are rendered in the application. It provides a display component for showing current configuration status and an editing interface for inputting configuration details.",
